Package controller

Class NonAdminController

java.lang.Object
controller.NonAdminController
public class NonAdminController
extends java.lang.Object
The non-admin controller allows regular users to manipulate their albums and view them as a list. Users can also search their photos
Author:
Wesley Cheung, Dennis Yu

    • start

      public void start​(User user, java.util.ArrayList<User> users)
      Starts the new scene for non-admin users. Takes in 2 parameters to load a user's data. The scene displays the list of user albums.
      Parameters:
      user - is the user that logged in
      users - is the list of users in the system. Used for serializing data.
